    PAE

    Triagem de documentos SEI⚓︎

    Informações gerais⚓︎

    Responsável Alessandro Campos
    E-mail alessandro.campos@meioambiente.mg.gov.br
    Desenvolvedora Isabela Romancini
    e-mail isabela.romancini@planejamento.mg.gov.br
    Ferramenta Power Automate Desktop
    Arquivo(s) auxiliar(es) PAE2.xlsx

    Funções desenvolvidas pelo robô⚓︎

    • Realiza pesquisa por número do documento SEI! e baixa o documento.
    • Descompacta arquivos e os salva no computador.
    • Verifica se há arquivos (PDF, shapefile e tif) corrompidos.
    • Verifica se há arquivos com formatos que não são aceitos para o PAE: KML, MPK e MXD;
    • Preenche planilhas de controle com as informações verificadas.
    Clique e veja o fluxo do robô
    graph TD; 1((Início))-->2; 2[Abrir planilha do excel]-->3; 3[Ver listagem de documentos SEI! da planilha do Excel ]-->4; 4[Copiar primeiro documento SEI!]-->5 5[Fazer login no SEI!]-->6 6[Buscar documento SEI!]-->7 7[Baixar documento]-->8 8[Descompactar arquivos]-->9 9[Salvar arquivos descompactados]-->10 10[Preencher Excel sobre documento baixado e descompactação dos arquivos]-->11 11[Criar nova planilha Excel - Planilha Documentos]-->12 12[Verificar se há arquivos corrompidos]-->13 13[Preencher Planilha Documentos informando se arquivos estão corrompidos]-->14 14[Verificar processo SEI! em busca de formatos de arquivos não aceitos]-->15 15[Preencher Planilha Documentos informando se formatos dos arquivos é aceito]-->16 16{Mais um processo?} 16-->|Não|17 16-->|Sim|3 17((Fim))

    Montando o seu robô⚓︎

    Aqui temos um protótipo de robô. Ele só vai solucionar o seu problema se ajustado às suas necessidades. Portanto, você deverá adaptá-lo.

    Para dar vida ao seu robô, clique na caixa copiar e colar abaixo. Depois, copie e cole o código disponível em um novo fluxo Power Automate Desktop.

    Clique para copiar e colar 
    SET linha TO 2
Excel.LaunchExcel.LaunchAndOpenUnderExistingProcess Path: caminho_excel Visible: True ReadOnly: False Instance=> planilha_documentos
Excel.ReadFromExcel.ReadCell Instance: planilha_documentos StartColumn: $'''b''' StartRow: linha ReadAsText: False CellValue=> doc_sei
Excel.ReadFromExcel.ReadCell Instance: planilha_documentos StartColumn: $'''a''' StartRow: linha ReadAsText: False CellValue=> processo_sei
Excel.GetFirstFreeRowOnColumn Instance: planilha_documentos Column: $'''a''' FirstFreeRowOnColumn=> tamanho_planilha
WebAutomation.LaunchChrome.LaunchChrome Url: $'''https://www.sei.mg.gov.br/sip/login.php?sigla_orgao_sistema=GOVMG&sigla_sistema=SEI''' WindowState: WebAutomation.BrowserWindowState.Maximized ClearCache: False ClearCookies: False WaitForPageToLoadTimeout: 60 Timeout: 60 BrowserInstance=> chrome
MouseAndKeyboard.SendKeys.FocusAndSendKeysByInstanceOrHandle WindowInstance: chrome TextToSend: $'''%login_SEI%{Tab}%senha_sei%{Tab}%órgão%{Tab}{Return}''' DelayBetweenKeystrokes: 10 SendTextAsHardwareKeys: False
LOOP WHILE (linha) < (tamanho_planilha)
    WAIT (WebAutomation.WaitForWebPageContent.WebPageToContainText BrowserInstance: chrome Text: $'''Controle de Processos''')
    MouseAndKeyboard.SendKeys.FocusAndSendKeysByInstanceOrHandle WindowInstance: chrome TextToSend: $'''{Tab}{Tab}%doc_sei%{Return}''' DelayBetweenKeystrokes: 10 SendTextAsHardwareKeys: False
    WebAutomation.Click.Click BrowserInstance: chrome Control: appmask['Web Page \'h ... ccc567fd13\'']['Anchor \'aqui\''] ClickType: WebAutomation.ClickType.LeftClick MouseClick: True WaitForPageToLoadTimeout: 60 MousePositionRelativeToElement: WebAutomation.RectangleEdgePoint.MiddleCenter OffsetX: 0 OffsetY: 0
    WAIT (UIAutomation.WaitForWindow.ToOpenByTitleClass Title: $'''Salvar como''' Class: $'''''' FocusWindow: False)
    IF (Folder.IfFolderExists.Exists Path: $'''%caminho_pasta%\\%processo_sei%''') THEN
        MouseAndKeyboard.SendKeys.FocusAndSendKeys TextToSend: $'''%caminho_pasta%\\%processo_sei%\\%doc_sei%{Return}''' DelayBetweenKeystrokes: 10 SendTextAsHardwareKeys: False
    ELSE
        Folder.Create FolderPath: caminho_pasta FolderName: processo_sei Folder=> pasta_processo
        MouseAndKeyboard.SendKeys.FocusAndSendKeys TextToSend: $'''%caminho_pasta%\\%processo_sei%\\%doc_sei%{Return}''' DelayBetweenKeystrokes: 10 SendTextAsHardwareKeys: False
    END
    WAIT (File.WaitForFile.Created File: $'''%caminho_pasta%\\%processo_sei%\\%doc_sei%.zip''')
    Compression.UnzipFiles ArchivePath: $'''%caminho_pasta%\\%processo_sei%\\%doc_sei%.zip''' DestinationFolder: $'''%caminho_pasta%\\%processo_sei%'''
    File.Delete Files: $'''%caminho_pasta%\\%processo_sei%\\%doc_sei%.zip'''
    Folder.GetSubfolders Folder: $'''%caminho_pasta%\\%processo_sei%''' FolderFilter: $'''*''' IncludeSubfolders: True FailOnAccessDenied: True SortBy1: Folder.SortBy.NoSort SortDescending1: False SortBy2: Folder.SortBy.NoSort SortDescending2: False SortBy3: Folder.SortBy.NoSort SortDescending3: False Subfolders=> folders
    LOOP FOREACH pasta IN folders
        Folder.GetFiles Folder: pasta FileFilter: $'''*.zip''' IncludeSubfolders: True FailOnAccessDenied: True SortBy1: Folder.SortBy.NoSort SortDescending1: False SortBy2: Folder.SortBy.NoSort SortDescending2: False SortBy3: Folder.SortBy.NoSort SortDescending3: False Files=> arquivos_zip
        Folder.GetFiles Folder: pasta FileFilter: $'''*.rar''' IncludeSubfolders: True FailOnAccessDenied: True SortBy1: Folder.SortBy.NoSort SortDescending1: False SortBy2: Folder.SortBy.NoSort SortDescending2: False SortBy3: Folder.SortBy.NoSort SortDescending3: False Files=> arquivos_rar
        Folder.GetFiles Folder: pasta FileFilter: $'''*.7z''' IncludeSubfolders: True FailOnAccessDenied: True SortBy1: Folder.SortBy.NoSort SortDescending1: False SortBy2: Folder.SortBy.NoSort SortDescending2: False SortBy3: Folder.SortBy.NoSort SortDescending3: False Files=> arquivos_7z
        IF IsNotEmpty(arquivos_zip) THEN
            LOOP FOREACH item_zip IN arquivos_zip
                Compression.UnzipFiles ArchivePath: item_zip DestinationFolder: $'''%caminho_pasta%\\%processo_sei%'''
                DISABLE File.Delete Files: item_zip
            END
        END
        IF IsNotEmpty(arquivos_7z) THEN
            LOOP FOREACH item_7z IN arquivos_7z
                UIAutomation.Click.Click Element: appmask['TaskBar']['Button \'Pesquisar\' 3'] ClickType: UIAutomation.ClickType.LeftClick MousePositionRelativeToElement: UIAutomation.RectangleEdgePoint.MiddleCenter OffsetX: 0 OffsetY: 0
                MouseAndKeyboard.SendKeys.FocusAndSendKeys TextToSend: $'''executar''' DelayBetweenKeystrokes: 10 SendTextAsHardwareKeys: False
                WAIT 1
                MouseAndKeyboard.SendKeys.FocusAndSendKeys TextToSend: $'''{Return}''' DelayBetweenKeystrokes: 10 SendTextAsHardwareKeys: False
                WAIT 1
                MouseAndKeyboard.SendKeys.FocusAndSendKeys TextToSend: $'''%item_7z%{Return}''' DelayBetweenKeystrokes: 10 SendTextAsHardwareKeys: False
                WAIT 3
                MouseAndKeyboard.MoveMouseToImage.ClickImage Images: [imgrepo['Extrair 7zip']] SearchForImageOn: MouseAndKeyboard.SearchTarget.EntireScreen MousePositionOnImage: MouseAndKeyboard.PositionOnImage.MiddleCenter OffsetX: 0 OffsetY: 0 Tolerance: 10 MovementStyle: MouseAndKeyboard.MovementStyle.Instant Occurence: 1 Timeout: 5 ClickType: MouseAndKeyboard.ClickType.LeftClick SecondsBeforeClick: 0 SearchAlgorithm: MouseAndKeyboard.ImageFinderAlgorithm.Legacy X=> X3 Y=> Y3
                DISABLE Text.CropText.CropTextBeforeFlag Text: item_rar ToFlag: $'''.rar''' IgnoreCase: False CroppedText=> Nome_pasta_7z IsFlagFound=> IsFlagFound
                MouseAndKeyboard.SendKeys.FocusAndSendKeys TextToSend: $'''%caminho_pasta%\\%processo_sei%{Return}''' DelayBetweenKeystrokes: 10 SendTextAsHardwareKeys: False
                WAIT 2
                IF (UIAutomation.IfWindow.IsOpenByTitleClass Title: $'''Confirmar a Substituição dos Arquivos''' Class: $'''''') THEN
                    UIAutomation.FocusWindow.FocusByTitleClass Title: $'''Confirmar a Substituição dos Arquivos''' Class: $''''''
                    WAIT 1
                    MouseAndKeyboard.SendKeys.FocusAndSendKeys TextToSend: $'''{Right}{Right}{Return}''' DelayBetweenKeystrokes: 100 SendTextAsHardwareKeys: False
                END
                MouseAndKeyboard.SendKeys.FocusAndSendKeys TextToSend: $'''{Alt}({F4})''' DelayBetweenKeystrokes: 10 SendTextAsHardwareKeys: False
                DISABLE File.Delete Files: item_7z
            END
        END
        IF IsNotEmpty(arquivos_rar) THEN
            LOOP FOREACH item_rar IN arquivos_rar
                UIAutomation.Click.Click Element: appmask['TaskBar']['Button \'Pesquisar\' 3'] ClickType: UIAutomation.ClickType.LeftClick MousePositionRelativeToElement: UIAutomation.RectangleEdgePoint.MiddleCenter OffsetX: 0 OffsetY: 0
                MouseAndKeyboard.SendKeys.FocusAndSendKeys TextToSend: $'''executar''' DelayBetweenKeystrokes: 10 SendTextAsHardwareKeys: False
                WAIT 1
                MouseAndKeyboard.SendKeys.FocusAndSendKeys TextToSend: $'''{Return}''' DelayBetweenKeystrokes: 10 SendTextAsHardwareKeys: False
                WAIT 1
                MouseAndKeyboard.SendKeys.FocusAndSendKeys TextToSend: $'''%item_rar%{Return}''' DelayBetweenKeystrokes: 10 SendTextAsHardwareKeys: False
                WAIT 4
                MouseAndKeyboard.MoveMouseToImage.ClickImage Images: [imgrepo['Extrair 7zip']] SearchForImageOn: MouseAndKeyboard.SearchTarget.EntireScreen MousePositionOnImage: MouseAndKeyboard.PositionOnImage.MiddleCenter OffsetX: 0 OffsetY: 0 Tolerance: 10 MovementStyle: MouseAndKeyboard.MovementStyle.Instant Occurence: 1 Timeout: 5 ClickType: MouseAndKeyboard.ClickType.LeftClick SecondsBeforeClick: 0 SearchAlgorithm: MouseAndKeyboard.ImageFinderAlgorithm.Legacy X=> X3 Y=> Y3
                DISABLE Text.CropText.CropTextBeforeFlag Text: item_rar ToFlag: $'''.rar''' IgnoreCase: False CroppedText=> Nome_pasta_rar IsFlagFound=> IsFlagFound
                MouseAndKeyboard.SendKeys.FocusAndSendKeys TextToSend: $'''%caminho_pasta%\\%processo_sei%{Return}''' DelayBetweenKeystrokes: 10 SendTextAsHardwareKeys: False
                WAIT 2
                IF (UIAutomation.IfWindow.IsOpenByTitleClass Title: $'''Confirmar a Substituição dos Arquivos''' Class: $'''''') THEN
                    UIAutomation.FocusWindow.FocusByTitleClass Title: $'''Confirmar a Substituição dos Arquivos''' Class: $''''''
                    WAIT 1
                    MouseAndKeyboard.SendKeys.FocusAndSendKeys TextToSend: $'''{Right}{Right}{Return}''' DelayBetweenKeystrokes: 100 SendTextAsHardwareKeys: False
                END
                MouseAndKeyboard.SendKeys.FocusAndSendKeys TextToSend: $'''{Alt}({F4})''' DelayBetweenKeystrokes: 10 SendTextAsHardwareKeys: False
                DISABLE File.Delete Files: item_rar
            END
        END
    END
    Excel.WriteToExcel.WriteCell Instance: planilha_documentos Value: $'''Arquivo baixado e descompactado''' Column: $'''c''' Row: linha
    WebAutomation.Click.Click BrowserInstance: chrome Control: appmask['Web Page \'h ... 171f2f165b\'']['Image \'Controle de Processos\''] ClickType: WebAutomation.ClickType.LeftClick MouseClick: True WaitForPageToLoadTimeout: 60 MousePositionRelativeToElement: WebAutomation.RectangleEdgePoint.MiddleCenter OffsetX: 0 OffsetY: 0
    Variables.IncreaseVariable Value: linha IncrementValue: 1
END
SET linha TO 2
LOOP WHILE (linha) < (tamanho_planilha)
    # Abrir arquivos shp. Obs: não tem como ter arquivos shapefile na pasta principal, porque não é possível inserí-los diretamente no SEI.
    Excel.ReadFromExcel.ReadCell Instance: planilha_documentos StartColumn: $'''a''' StartRow: linha ReadAsText: False CellValue=> processo_sei
    Excel.LaunchExcel.LaunchUnderExistingProcess Visible: True Instance=> planilha_processo
    Excel.RenameWorksheet.RenameWorksheetWithIndex Instance: planilha_processo Index: 1 NewName: processo_sei
    Excel.SetActiveWorksheet.ActivateWorksheetByName Instance: planilha_processo Name: processo_sei
    Excel.WriteToExcel.WriteCell Instance: planilha_processo Value: $'''Processo SEI %processo_sei%''' Column: $'''A''' Row: 1
    Excel.WriteToExcel.WriteCell Instance: planilha_processo Value: $'''Nome arquivo''' Column: $'''A''' Row: 2
    Excel.WriteToExcel.WriteCell Instance: planilha_processo Value: $'''Status''' Column: $'''B''' Row: 2
    SET linha_excel TO 3
    # Abrir arquivos
    Folder.GetFiles Folder: $'''%caminho_pasta%\\%processo_sei%''' FileFilter: $'''*.pdf''' IncludeSubfolders: True FailOnAccessDenied: True SortBy1: Folder.SortBy.NoSort SortDescending1: False SortBy2: Folder.SortBy.NoSort SortDescending2: False SortBy3: Folder.SortBy.NoSort SortDescending3: False Files=> arquivos_pdf
    IF IsNotEmpty(arquivos_pdf) THEN
        LOOP FOREACH item_pdf IN arquivos_pdf
            UIAutomation.Click.Click Element: appmask['TaskBar']['Button \'Pesquisar\' 2'] ClickType: UIAutomation.ClickType.LeftClick MousePositionRelativeToElement: UIAutomation.RectangleEdgePoint.MiddleCenter OffsetX: 0 OffsetY: 0
            WAIT 2
            MouseAndKeyboard.SendKeys.FocusAndSendKeys TextToSend: $'''EXECUTAR''' DelayBetweenKeystrokes: 10 SendTextAsHardwareKeys: False
            WAIT 2
            MouseAndKeyboard.SendKeys.FocusAndSendKeys TextToSend: $'''{Return}''' DelayBetweenKeystrokes: 10 SendTextAsHardwareKeys: False
            WAIT (UIAutomation.WaitForWindow.ToOpenByTitleClass Title: $'''Executar''' Class: $'''''' FocusWindow: False)
            MouseAndKeyboard.SendKeys.FocusAndSendKeys TextToSend: $'''%item_pdf%{Return}''' DelayBetweenKeystrokes: 10 SendTextAsHardwareKeys: False
            File.GetPathPart File: item_pdf RootPath=> RootPath Directory=> Directory FileName=> FileName FileNameWithoutExtension=> FileNameNoExtension Extension=> FileExtension
            WAIT (UIAutomation.WaitForWindow.ToOpenByTitleClass Title: $'''%FileName% - Adobe Acrobat Reader (64-bit)''' Class: $'''''' FocusWindow: False)
            WAIT 5
            IF (UIAutomation.IfImage.ExistsOnScreen Images: [imgrepo['Image_2']] FindAllImages: False Tolerance: 10 SearchAlgorithm: UIAutomation.ImageFinderAlgorithm.Legacy) THEN
                Excel.WriteToExcel.WriteCell Instance: planilha_processo Value: item_pdf Column: $'''A''' Row: linha_excel
                Excel.WriteToExcel.WriteCell Instance: planilha_processo Value: $'''Corrompido''' Column: $'''B''' Row: linha_excel
                MouseAndKeyboard.SendKeys.FocusAndSendKeys TextToSend: $'''{Alt}({F4})''' DelayBetweenKeystrokes: 10 SendTextAsHardwareKeys: False
            ELSE
                Excel.WriteToExcel.WriteCell Instance: planilha_processo Value: item_pdf Column: $'''A''' Row: linha_excel
                Excel.WriteToExcel.WriteCell Instance: planilha_processo Value: $'''Arquivo abre no leitor de PDF''' Column: $'''B''' Row: linha_excel
            END
            Variables.IncreaseVariable Value: linha_excel IncrementValue: 1
            MouseAndKeyboard.SendKeys.FocusAndSendKeysByTitleClass Title: $'''%FileName% - Adobe Acrobat Reader (64-bit)''' Class: $'''''' TextToSend: $'''{Alt}({F4})''' DelayBetweenKeystrokes: 10 SendTextAsHardwareKeys: False
        END
    END
    /# obter de novo as pastas e subpastas
#/
    LOOP FOREACH pasta IN folders
        Folder.GetFiles Folder: pasta FileFilter: $'''*.kml''' IncludeSubfolders: True FailOnAccessDenied: True SortBy1: Folder.SortBy.NoSort SortDescending1: False SortBy2: Folder.SortBy.NoSort SortDescending2: False SortBy3: Folder.SortBy.NoSort SortDescending3: False Files=> arquivos_kml
        Folder.GetFiles Folder: pasta FileFilter: $'''*.mxd''' IncludeSubfolders: True FailOnAccessDenied: True SortBy1: Folder.SortBy.NoSort SortDescending1: False SortBy2: Folder.SortBy.NoSort SortDescending2: False SortBy3: Folder.SortBy.NoSort SortDescending3: False Files=> arquivos_mxd
        Folder.GetFiles Folder: pasta FileFilter: $'''*.mpk''' IncludeSubfolders: True FailOnAccessDenied: True SortBy1: Folder.SortBy.NoSort SortDescending1: False SortBy2: Folder.SortBy.NoSort SortDescending2: False SortBy3: Folder.SortBy.NoSort SortDescending3: False Files=> arquivos_mpk
        Folder.GetFiles Folder: pasta FileFilter: $'''*.pdf''' IncludeSubfolders: True FailOnAccessDenied: True SortBy1: Folder.SortBy.NoSort SortDescending1: False SortBy2: Folder.SortBy.NoSort SortDescending2: False SortBy3: Folder.SortBy.NoSort SortDescending3: False Files=> arquivos_pdf
        IF IsNotEmpty(arquivos_kml) THEN
            LOOP FOREACH item_kml IN arquivos_kml
                Excel.WriteToExcel.WriteCell Instance: planilha_processo Value: item_kml Column: $'''A''' Row: linha_excel
                Excel.WriteToExcel.WriteCell Instance: planilha_processo Value: $'''Arquivo kml - solicitar outro nos formatos do TR''' Column: $'''B''' Row: linha_excel
                Variables.IncreaseVariable Value: linha_excel IncrementValue: 1
            END
        END
        IF IsNotEmpty(arquivos_mxd) THEN
            LOOP FOREACH item_mxd IN arquivos_mxd
                Excel.WriteToExcel.WriteCell Instance: planilha_processo Value: item_mxd Column: $'''A''' Row: linha_excel
                Excel.WriteToExcel.WriteCell Instance: planilha_processo Value: $'''Arquivo mdt - solicitar outro nos formatos do TR''' Column: $'''B''' Row: linha_excel
                Variables.IncreaseVariable Value: linha_excel IncrementValue: 1
            END
        END
        IF IsNotEmpty(arquivos_mpk) THEN
            LOOP FOREACH item_mpk IN arquivos_mpk
                Excel.WriteToExcel.WriteCell Instance: planilha_processo Value: item_mpk Column: $'''A''' Row: linha_excel
                Excel.WriteToExcel.WriteCell Instance: planilha_processo Value: $'''Arquivo mpk- solicitar outro nos formatos do TR''' Column: $'''B''' Row: linha_excel
                Variables.IncreaseVariable Value: linha_excel IncrementValue: 1
            END
        END
        IF IsNotEmpty(arquivos_pdf) THEN
            LOOP FOREACH item_pdf IN arquivos_pdf
                UIAutomation.Click.Click Element: appmask['TaskBar']['Button \'Pesquisar\' 2'] ClickType: UIAutomation.ClickType.LeftClick MousePositionRelativeToElement: UIAutomation.RectangleEdgePoint.MiddleCenter OffsetX: 0 OffsetY: 0
                WAIT 2
                MouseAndKeyboard.SendKeys.FocusAndSendKeys TextToSend: $'''EXECUTAR''' DelayBetweenKeystrokes: 10 SendTextAsHardwareKeys: False
                WAIT 2
                MouseAndKeyboard.SendKeys.FocusAndSendKeys TextToSend: $'''{Return}''' DelayBetweenKeystrokes: 10 SendTextAsHardwareKeys: False
                WAIT (UIAutomation.WaitForWindow.ToOpenByTitleClass Title: $'''Executar''' Class: $'''''' FocusWindow: False)
                MouseAndKeyboard.SendKeys.FocusAndSendKeys TextToSend: $'''%item_pdf%{Return}''' DelayBetweenKeystrokes: 10 SendTextAsHardwareKeys: False
                File.GetPathPart File: item_pdf RootPath=> RootPath Directory=> Directory FileName=> FileName FileNameWithoutExtension=> FileNameNoExtension Extension=> FileExtension
                WAIT (UIAutomation.WaitForWindow.ToOpenByTitleClass Title: $'''%FileName% - Adobe Acrobat Reader (64-bit)''' Class: $'''''' FocusWindow: False)
                WAIT 5
                IF (UIAutomation.IfImage.ExistsOnScreen Images: [imgrepo['Image_2']] FindAllImages: False Tolerance: 10 SearchAlgorithm: UIAutomation.ImageFinderAlgorithm.Legacy) THEN
                    Excel.WriteToExcel.WriteCell Instance: planilha_processo Value: item_pdf Column: $'''A''' Row: linha_excel
                    Excel.WriteToExcel.WriteCell Instance: planilha_processo Value: $'''Corrompido''' Column: $'''B''' Row: linha_excel
                    MouseAndKeyboard.SendKeys.FocusAndSendKeys TextToSend: $'''{Alt}({F4})''' DelayBetweenKeystrokes: 10 SendTextAsHardwareKeys: False
                ELSE
                    Excel.WriteToExcel.WriteCell Instance: planilha_processo Value: item_pdf Column: $'''A''' Row: linha_excel
                    Excel.WriteToExcel.WriteCell Instance: planilha_processo Value: $'''Arquivo abre no leitor de PDF''' Column: $'''B''' Row: linha_excel
                END
                Variables.IncreaseVariable Value: linha_excel IncrementValue: 1
                MouseAndKeyboard.SendKeys.FocusAndSendKeysByTitleClass Title: $'''%FileName% - Adobe Acrobat Reader (64-bit)''' Class: $'''''' TextToSend: $'''{Alt}({F4})''' DelayBetweenKeystrokes: 10 SendTextAsHardwareKeys: False
            END
        END
        Folder.GetFiles Folder: pasta FileFilter: $'''*.shp''' IncludeSubfolders: True FailOnAccessDenied: True SortBy1: Folder.SortBy.NoSort SortDescending1: False SortBy2: Folder.SortBy.NoSort SortDescending2: False SortBy3: Folder.SortBy.NoSort SortDescending3: False Files=> arquivos_shp
        Folder.GetFiles Folder: pasta FileFilter: $'''*.tif''' IncludeSubfolders: True FailOnAccessDenied: True SortBy1: Folder.SortBy.NoSort SortDescending1: False SortBy2: Folder.SortBy.NoSort SortDescending2: False SortBy3: Folder.SortBy.NoSort SortDescending3: False Files=> arquivos_tif
        IF IsNotEmpty(arquivos_shp) THEN
            LOOP FOREACH testearquivo IN arquivos_shp
                # Mudar FEAM
                UIAutomation.Click.Click Element: appmask['TaskBar']['Button \'Pesquisar\' 2'] ClickType: UIAutomation.ClickType.LeftClick MousePositionRelativeToElement: UIAutomation.RectangleEdgePoint.MiddleCenter OffsetX: 0 OffsetY: 0
                WAIT 2
                MouseAndKeyboard.SendKeys.FocusAndSendKeys TextToSend: $'''EXECUTAR''' DelayBetweenKeystrokes: 10 SendTextAsHardwareKeys: False
                WAIT 2
                MouseAndKeyboard.SendKeys.FocusAndSendKeys TextToSend: $'''{Return}''' DelayBetweenKeystrokes: 10 SendTextAsHardwareKeys: False
                WAIT (UIAutomation.WaitForWindow.ToOpenByTitleClass Title: $'''Executar''' Class: $'''''' FocusWindow: False)
                MouseAndKeyboard.SendKeys.FocusAndSendKeys TextToSend: $'''%testearquivo%{Return}''' DelayBetweenKeystrokes: 10 SendTextAsHardwareKeys: False
                # Considerando Qgis em português
                DISABLE WAIT (UIAutomation.WaitForWindow.ToOpenByTitleClass Title: $'''*Projeto sem título — QGIS''' Class: $'''''' FocusWindow: False)
                # Considerando Qgis em inglês
                WAIT (UIAutomation.WaitForWindow.ToOpenByTitleClass Title: $'''*Untitled Project - QGIS''' Class: $'''''' FocusWindow: False)
                IF (UIAutomation.IfWindow.IsOpenByTitleClass Title: $'''Seletor de sistema de coordenadas de referência (SRC)''' Class: $'''''') THEN
                    MouseAndKeyboard.SendKeys.FocusAndSendKeysByTitleClass Title: $'''Seletor de sistema de coordenadas de referência (SRC)''' Class: $'''''' TextToSend: $'''{Return}''' DelayBetweenKeystrokes: 10 SendTextAsHardwareKeys: False
                END
                IF (UIAutomation.IfImage.ExistsOnScreen Images: [imgrepo['Image_4']] FindAllImages: False Tolerance: 10 SearchAlgorithm: UIAutomation.ImageFinderAlgorithm.Legacy) THEN
                    Excel.WriteToExcel.WriteCell Instance: planilha_processo Value: testearquivo Column: $'''A''' Row: linha_excel
                    Excel.WriteToExcel.WriteCell Instance: planilha_processo Value: $'''Corrompido''' Column: $'''B''' Row: linha_excel
                    # Considerando Qgis em português
                    DISABLE MouseAndKeyboard.SendKeys.FocusAndSendKeysByTitleClass Title: $'''*Projeto sem título — QGIS''' Class: $'''''' TextToSend: $'''{Alt}({F4})''' DelayBetweenKeystrokes: 10 SendTextAsHardwareKeys: False
                    # Considerando Qgis em inglês
                    MouseAndKeyboard.SendKeys.FocusAndSendKeysByTitleClass Title: $'''*Untitled Project - QGIS''' Class: $'''''' TextToSend: $'''{Alt}({F4})''' DelayBetweenKeystrokes: 10 SendTextAsHardwareKeys: False
                    GOTO 'Pular pós corrompido'
                ELSE
                    Excel.WriteToExcel.WriteCell Instance: planilha_processo Value: testearquivo Column: $'''A''' Row: linha_excel
                    Excel.WriteToExcel.WriteCell Instance: planilha_processo Value: $'''Arquivo abre no Qgis''' Column: $'''B''' Row: linha_excel
                END
                # Considerando Qgis em português
                DISABLE MouseAndKeyboard.SendKeys.FocusAndSendKeysByTitleClass Title: $'''*Projeto sem título — QGIS''' Class: $'''''' TextToSend: $'''{Alt}({F4})''' DelayBetweenKeystrokes: 10 SendTextAsHardwareKeys: False
                # Considerando Qgis em inglês
                WAIT 2
                MouseAndKeyboard.SendKeys.FocusAndSendKeysByTitleClass Title: $'''*Untitled Project - QGIS''' Class: $'''''' TextToSend: $'''{Alt}({F4})''' DelayBetweenKeystrokes: 10 SendTextAsHardwareKeys: False
                WAIT (UIAutomation.WaitForWindow.ToOpenByTitleClass Title: $'''Salvar Projeto''' Class: $'''''' FocusWindow: False)
                MouseAndKeyboard.SendKeys.FocusAndSendKeysByTitleClass Title: $'''Salvar Projeto''' Class: $'''''' TextToSend: $'''{Right}{Return}''' DelayBetweenKeystrokes: 10 SendTextAsHardwareKeys: False
                LABEL 'Pular pós corrompido'
                Variables.IncreaseVariable Value: linha_excel IncrementValue: 1
            END
        END
        IF IsNotEmpty(arquivos_tif) THEN
            LOOP FOREACH item_tif IN arquivos_tif
                UIAutomation.Click.Click Element: appmask['TaskBar']['Button \'Pesquisar\' 2'] ClickType: UIAutomation.ClickType.LeftClick MousePositionRelativeToElement: UIAutomation.RectangleEdgePoint.MiddleCenter OffsetX: 0 OffsetY: 0
                WAIT 2
                MouseAndKeyboard.SendKeys.FocusAndSendKeys TextToSend: $'''EXECUTAR''' DelayBetweenKeystrokes: 10 SendTextAsHardwareKeys: False
                WAIT 2
                MouseAndKeyboard.SendKeys.FocusAndSendKeys TextToSend: $'''{Return}''' DelayBetweenKeystrokes: 10 SendTextAsHardwareKeys: False
                WAIT (UIAutomation.WaitForWindow.ToOpenByTitleClass Title: $'''Executar''' Class: $'''''' FocusWindow: False)
                MouseAndKeyboard.SendKeys.FocusAndSendKeys TextToSend: $'''%item_tif%{Return}''' DelayBetweenKeystrokes: 10 SendTextAsHardwareKeys: False
                # Considerando Qgis em português
                DISABLE WAIT (UIAutomation.WaitForWindow.ToOpenByTitleClass Title: $'''*Projeto sem título — QGIS''' Class: $'''''' FocusWindow: False)
                # Considerando Qgis em inglês
                WAIT (UIAutomation.WaitForWindow.ToOpenByTitleClass Title: $'''*Untitled Project - QGIS''' Class: $'''''' FocusWindow: False)
                IF (UIAutomation.IfImage.ExistsOnScreen Images: [imgrepo['Image_2']] FindAllImages: False Tolerance: 10 SearchAlgorithm: UIAutomation.ImageFinderAlgorithm.Legacy) THEN
                    Excel.WriteToExcel.WriteCell Instance: planilha_processo Value: item_tif Column: $'''A''' Row: linha_excel
                    Excel.WriteToExcel.WriteCell Instance: planilha_processo Value: $'''Corrompido''' Column: $'''B''' Row: linha_excel
                ELSE
                    Excel.WriteToExcel.WriteCell Instance: planilha_processo Value: item_tif Column: $'''A''' Row: linha_excel
                    Excel.WriteToExcel.WriteCell Instance: planilha_processo Value: $'''Arquivo abre no Qgis''' Column: $'''B''' Row: linha_excel
                END
                Variables.IncreaseVariable Value: linha_excel IncrementValue: 1
                # Considerando Qgis em português
                DISABLE MouseAndKeyboard.SendKeys.FocusAndSendKeysByTitleClass Title: $'''*Projeto sem título — QGIS''' Class: $'''''' TextToSend: $'''{Alt}({F4})''' DelayBetweenKeystrokes: 10 SendTextAsHardwareKeys: False
                # Considerando Qgis em inglês
                MouseAndKeyboard.SendKeys.FocusAndSendKeysByTitleClass Title: $'''*Untitled Project - QGIS''' Class: $'''''' TextToSend: $'''{Alt}({F4})''' DelayBetweenKeystrokes: 10 SendTextAsHardwareKeys: False
                WAIT (UIAutomation.WaitForWindow.ToOpenByTitleClass Title: $'''Salvar Projeto''' Class: $'''''' FocusWindow: False)
                MouseAndKeyboard.SendKeys.FocusAndSendKeysByTitleClass Title: $'''Salvar Projeto''' Class: $'''''' TextToSend: $'''{Right}{Return}''' DelayBetweenKeystrokes: 10 SendTextAsHardwareKeys: False
            END
        END
    END
    WebAutomation.CloseWebBrowser BrowserInstance: chrome
    Excel.CloseExcel.CloseAndSaveAs Instance: planilha_processo DocumentFormat: Excel.ExcelFormat.FromExtension DocumentPath: $'''%caminho_pasta%\\%processo_sei%'''
    Variables.IncreaseVariable Value: linha IncrementValue: 1
    Excel.SaveExcel.Save Instance: planilha_documentos
END
Display.ShowMessageDialog.ShowMessage Title: $'''Concluído''' Message: $'''Fluxo concluído''' Icon: Display.Icon.None Buttons: Display.Buttons.OK DefaultButton: Display.DefaultButton.Button1 IsTopMost: False ButtonPressed=> ButtonPressed

    Importante:

    Antes de executar este robô em especial, é importante seguir os seguintes passos:

    1. Verificar se a máquina em que o robô vai ser executado possui os seguintes programas instalados:
      • Microsoft Power Automate;
      • Extensão do Google Chrome ("Microsoft Power Automate" - sem ser o legacy);
      • 7-zip;
      • QGis.
    2. Criar planilha-base no Excel: "Número do processo SEI" na célula 1A, "Número do documento SEI" na 1B e "Status" na 1C;
    3. Alterar configurações da pasta "download" para baixar arquivos numa pasta separada;
    4. Configurar como padrão:
      • Abrir arquivos em PDF no Adobe Acrobat;
      • Abrir arquivos shapefile no QGis;
      • Descompactar arquivos no 7-zip.

    Caso precise de ajuda

    Algum erro está ocorrendo em uma das fases de criação de seu robô? Não tem problema. Abaixo temos um espaço para perguntas e respostas. Dá uma olhadinha lá. Quem sabe alguém já não fez uma pergunta com o mesmo problema que você está enfrentando. Caso prefira mande um e-mail para escolher-email@dominio.com.
